<paragraph blockId="47.[714,1247,1022,1301]" pageId="47" pageNumber="106">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="47" pageNumber="106">
Plantae 5-8(-12) cm altae, foliis plerumque caule longioribus, cormo ovoideo 
<quantity box="[967,1063,1048,1072]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="8.0" pageId="47" pageNumber="106" unit="mm" value="9.0" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="8.0">8-10 mm</quantity>
diam., foliis filiformibus in sectione transversali ovalibus 4-sulcatis, pilosis, 
<quantity box="[781,877,1098,1122]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.75" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="47" pageNumber="106" unit="mm" value="1.75" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.5">1.5-2 mm</quantity>
diam., inflorescentiae bracteis viridibus exterioribus 
<quantity box="[834,940,1124,1148]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.15" metricValueMax="2.5" metricValueMin="1.8" pageId="47" pageNumber="106" unit="mm" value="21.5" valueMax="25.0" valueMin="18.0">18-25 mm</quantity>
longis, interioribus marginibus late scariosis, floribus albis saepe pallide purpureonotatis prope basem tepalorum externorum, tubo perianthii cylindrico 
<quantity box="[812,917,1200,1224]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.65" metricValueMax="3.3" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="47" pageNumber="106" unit="mm" value="26.5" valueMax="33.0" valueMin="20.0">20-33 mm</quantity>
longo, tepalis 12-16(-20)
</emphasis>
× 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="47" pageNumber="106">
<quantity metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.25" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="2.5" pageId="47" pageNumber="106" unit="mm" value="3.25" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="2.5">2.5-4 mm</quantity>
, laxe patentibus, filamentis c. 
<quantity box="[1041,1099,1225,1249]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="47" pageNumber="106" unit="mm" value="4.0">4 mm</quantity>
longis, antheris erectis contiguis 
<quantity box="[868,946,1251,1276]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="6.0" pageId="47" pageNumber="106" unit="mm" value="6.5" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="6.0">6-7 mm</quantity>
longis atropurpureis, pollinibus rubrobrunneis.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
